00:18:11,720 --> 00:18:12,920
It's all right.

300
00:18:20,000 --> 00:18:21,460
Mister...

301
00:18:24,280 --> 00:18:25,280
To put it simply,

302
00:18:25,670 --> 00:18:28,030
